cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.CY, cs.LG

The paper discusses the design and evaluation of an AI-driven game level editor, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The tool is used for creating game levels, which falls under graphics (cs.GR) and cybernetics (cs.CY). The study also involves analyzing data and drawing conclusions, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG).
